       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. SOLUTION.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
           01 A        PIC 9(10)   VALUE ZEROES.
           01 B        PIC 9(10)   VALUE ZEROES.
           01 STR      PIC X(10).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           ACCEPT STR
           MOVE STR TO A
           ACCEPT STR
           MOVE STR TO B
           ADD A TO B
           MOVE B TO STR
           INSPECT STR REPLACING LEADING "0" by " "
           DISPLAY STR
       STOP RUN.